data.title: InAxtion: most succesful business of the year?
data.text:
That's something we've secretly been dreaming about for some time. Will you help us win the National Business Success Award 2015? We've already been nominated. Now we are going for gold.

On the 6th of February in Studio 21 in Hilversum, Dutch ex-prime minister Jan Peter Balkenende will present a number of themed awards as well as a € 100,000 prize.

VOTING IS FREE, BUT HURRY, the lines close at midnight on the 16th of January. How does it work? Send a text message: NBSA 5972 to 4422. Your text is fee, you will just be charged € 0.25 for the confirmation message to tell you that your vote has been received. Will you vote for InAxtion?

Many thanks.
